ng a Harry Potter book together, and they\'ve also been doing Harry Potter-related tasks. Josh\'s a little excited to tell us that he\'ll be going to the theater to play a concert.',NULL,NULL),(64296,12585,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2020/09/07/CFRU Mobile Community Radio Show - September 7, 2020 at 13:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2020-09-07 13:00:00',86638720,'2023-12-05 13:47:17',NULL,'This week\'s guest on the Blenders Public show is a man named Jean. He\'s a self-made millionaire who works for a charity called the Community of Hearts. He listens to community radio every day. This week, he listens to a show called \"Community of Hearts\" with Josh, Duncan, and Amanda.\n\nThe first segment of the show is devoted to a song called \"Noya\" by Shania Twain. Josh and Duncan talk about the singer, who is well-known for her big voice. Duncan says he likes her music, too, and that he likes Shania\'s concerts. Josh asks Duncan what he likes to do while he\'s at home. Duncan likes puzzles, reading, and movies. Josh likes to play with animals, like snakes.',NULL,NULL),(64297,12585,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2020/08/31/CFRU Mobile Community Radio Show - August 31, 2020 at 13:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2020-08-31 13:00:00',86638720,'2023-12-05 13:28:02',NULL,'This week on the CFRU 93.1 FM community radio show, the Host and Host\'s friends Duncan and Josh discuss their favorite songs, the music they listen to, and all the other things they do. The Host goes back to the Community of Hearts to talk to Josh, who is planning to go to a movie tonight. He also asks if he can stay home on Sunday because his brother is going to be bad. Josh says he can\'t because he\'s going to watch a movie.',NULL,NULL),(64298,12585,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2020/08/24/CFRU Mobile Community Radio Show - August 24, 2020 at 13:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2020-08-24 13:00:00',86638720,'2023-12-05 13:14:53',NULL,'The Merry Mask Makers is a project started by the Guelph tool library to create free masks for 