11-07 10:00:00',86507648,'2023-11-10 08:28:35',NULL,'The guys talk about the McCrackens, a band from New York City that\'s one of the best-selling indie acts of all-time. The band\'s first album, Tommy the Chicken from Gob, was actually released in the same year as Tommy\'s debut album, What Came First, which was a huge hit. The guys agree that it\'s awesome that guitarists can play the drums and that drummers can understand how to play the other instruments. The group\'s drummer, Spot, is a dog, which means he\'s the better drummer. So, listen to the band. If you like the band, then you can listen to them, even if you hate them. But if you like them, you can\'t just listen to their music. You have to support them through your music. Sounds like a good idea, right? According to the Canadian Medical Association, one in eight people will die without a living donor of their own. So if you want to save someone\'s life, you\'ve got to register. You can become a donor by going to BeAdonor.ca.',NULL,'How to become a living donor in Canada (13 minute read)'),(68898,2653,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/11/07/Solipsistic Retreat - November 7, 2023 at 09:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-11-07 09:00:00',86507648,'2023-11-10 08:19:41',NULL,'The boys are back from their trip to their friends and family and they\'re listening to a program called \"Solipsistic Retreat\" on CFRU 93.2. They\'re talking about a band called Rec Center and there\'s also a solo band called the Ramones. Tommy Ramone is one of the original members of the band, and he\'s been making music since the \'80s. The boys say they\'ve listened to a lot of music, including the Ramones, and they all have a favorite Ramone. One of the boys says he was told the Ramones were like Green Day, but he couldn\'t listen to them because he was too young to understand how seriously they took their music. He says he cried when he heard the Ramones say he cried and he cried, but eventually he realized that the joke was his friends