roud of him. Ken and his father are very close. They have a very close relationship.',NULL,NULL),(69440,196,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/s26cwr/November_19_2023_Across_the_Universeaqfej.mp3','2023-11-20 21:10:51',431961989,'2023-11-21 01:49:51','2023-11-20 23:05:37','The sound of your City fundraising campaign. The last day of On-Air Campaign. The Host of CIUT.fm announces that it is the final day of the campaign. He hopes listeners will come in and donate. He also invites listeners to listen more than they usually do.\n\nHe explains that the station is a unique, free, and open format and that he wants listeners to value what they hear on the station. He adds that they should call and donate at CIUT and listen to the music.\n\nThe Basement freaks are going to perform a track called \"Hit the Flame\" as they get to the end of the show. He asks listeners to call and give. He thanks all the listeners who have already donated. He then thanks Neil Pratt and Graham Benfield for their financial contribution.',NULL,NULL),(69441,257,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/ag49k5/November_16_2023_Psychedelic_Stoner_Rocka17bo.mp3','2023-11-20 21:12:49',287962512,'2023-11-21 01:50:47','2023-11-20 23:05:50','The next Thursday night program is heard, and the host is Lee Ronaldo\'s son, Sage. Ken says he\'s a huge fan of the program, and he tells us that it\'s going to be a big hit.\n\nHe also says that they\'re doing a big tour of the building during the fall fundraiser, and that they need your help. They\'re asking listeners to give them a call or go to their website, where they can donate.Ken then announces the program\'s start time. He starts off by playing the track \"Sergeant Taurus on Poke\" and then proceeds to play \"The Space Huns.\" Ken says they need the phone donation lines and the donation site to be really busy right now.',NULL,NULL),(69442,292,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/rcumdw/November_17_2023_The_Cool_Side_of_the_Pillow9gy4h.mp3','2023-11-20 21:08:44',287962512